WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.744
Shamir, ant-sized, declared, 'Size

00:03.744 --> 00:04.186
matters not!

00:04.186 --> 00:04.627
' Flashback:

00:04.627 --> 00:04.848
Underground

00:04.848 --> 00:09.240
fighting memories, brutal and

00:09.240 --> 00:13.488
swift, like the Winter

00:13.488 --> 00:13.716
Soldier.

00:13.716 --> 00:14.400
A musical chairs

00:14.400 --> 00:16.320
sequence showed the Prime

00:16.320 --> 00:18.576
Minister's throne switching with

00:18.576 --> 00:19.014
Peres's;

00:19.014 --> 00:20.328
a dramatic swap!

00:20.328 --> 00:23.136
Intifada panels flashed:

00:23.136 --> 00:24.072
stones

00:24.072 --> 00:26.328
against tanks, David versus

00:26.328 --> 00:26.622
Goliath;

00:26.622 --> 00:27.504
a clang of

00:27.504 --> 00:27.816
desperate conflict.

00:27.816 --> 00:28.128
He was

00:28.128 --> 00:31.248
dragged to the Madrid

00:31.248 --> 00:33.384
Conference, a desperate plea

00:33.384 --> 00:34.378
escaping him, 'No!

00:34.378 --> 00:35.040
' Bush

00:35.040 --> 00:35.928
Senior loomed, a mega-threat.

00:35.928 --> 00:36.648
'Your loans...

00:36.648 --> 00:37.008
gone!

00:37.008 --> 00:37.728
' An

00:37.728 --> 00:40.176
immovable object panel declared,

00:40.176 --> 00:40.738
'Not one inch!

00:40.738 --> 00:41.112
' It

00:41.112 --> 00:41.640
met an unstoppable force;

00:41.640 --> 00:41.725
a catastrophic crash.

00:41.725 --> 00:41.753
Defeat:

00:41.753 --> 00:41.867
votes scattered like dust.

00:41.867 --> 00:42.037
He declared, his voice booming, 'Terror?

00:42.037 --> 00:42.122
I invented it!

00:42.122 --> 00:42.236
' A mic drop.

00:42.236 --> 00:42.264
BOOM!

